branchCategory.name: 90-JS, Floating Joint, Stainless Steel
branchCategory.description: <p>Floating joint series 90-JS is made of stainless steel and used to increase corrosion resistance. JS uses a dust cover made of fluoro rubber or  silicon rubber and is shaped to prevent residual liquid, therefore sealing is improved.  Overall length as well as maximum tension and compression are the same as standard series JA. 90-JS is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing.</p>
